items.title: Trump signs sweeping tax and spending bill into law
items.description: A signing ceremony at the White House on Friday afternoon kicked off celebrations for 4 July.

items.title: Hamas says it delivered 'positive response' on Gaza ceasefire plan
items.description: The group said it was ready to begin negotiations immediately after Donald Trump said Israel had accepted conditions for a 60-day ceasefire.

items.title: Sport agent Jonathan Barnett accused of rape in US lawsuit
